Vidi,is,a,service,that,lets,developers,add,live,streaming,video,to,their,web,sites,and,applications,The,video,capability,can,be,used,for,video,conferencing,video,messaging,video,chat,live,broadcasts,security,cameras,and,more,The,API,lets,developers,control,aspects,of,the,video,feed,such,as,the,room,client,player,and,more,The,API,uses,REST,SOAP,and,JavaScript,protocols,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON